9 June 2011Members of the media, who have applied for accreditation for the funeral of the late Mama Albertina Sisulu, are advised to collect their accreditation cards at the Presidential Suite at Orlando Stadium in Soweto.The accreditation centre will open from: Date: 9 - 10 June 2011 Time: 14h00 - 19h00Individual journalists must personally present themselves to collect accreditation. Identification such as an ID book/passport will be required for easy identification and collection.Enquiries: Bongiwe Gambu Cell: 082 714 9463Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)